          "slidetitle": "Securing Your Connected Site",
          "subtitle": "Practical steps to reduce cyber exposure.",
          "slidecontent": "• Segment your site network so that IoT devices sit separately from core business systems\n• Change default passwords immediately on every connected device\n• Keep firmware updated\n• Limit remote access to authorised personnel only, using multi-factor authentication\n• Audit connected devices regularly to spot anything unfamiliar or unauthorised\n• Train site staff to recognise suspicious activity, not just IT teams"
