          "subtitle": "Limit Access, Patch Systems Regularly",
          "slidecontent": "• Every connected device on site is a potential entry point for attackers\n• Fewer open access points means less risk\n• Remove or disable any devices, accounts, or software no longer in active use\n• Apply security patches and firmware updates to all smart tools and systems as soon as they are released\n• Restrict who can log in to site networks, using strong passwords and multi-factor authentication\n• Regularly audit which devices are connected and revoke access that is no longer needed"
